Invocation Name: wasco facts
des:
Ask for Wasco Facts, and learn about the small town in California.

Wasco Facts provides interesting nuggets about the town in Central California.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Wasco Facts" or "Alexa, open Wasco Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
